page.title: 05Vanessa George
page.content: {In the morning I woke up,went to {the toilet then read a book. {I had my breakfast at 7.30.I went in {the bathroom then I got dressed.I {walked up to school at 8.30.at 8.59 we {came into the classroom and had the {register.We had assembly and a few {people did a play.I walked up the {steps and we worked.At 10.40 we went {outside for break.At 11.00 we worked {until lunchtime.At 12.20 I went on the {log cabin.After that I played football {rounders, but then I went to make a {daisy chain.We came in and had silent {reading from 1.03 until 1.28.At 1.30 {we worked until 3.00,I walked home at {3.03.When I got home I had a packet of {crisps and I read the Newbury Weekly {News.I watched T.V. at 5.00.At 7.00 I {went to Guides.After Guides I had a {bath.At 8.59 I got into bed and my mum {came in to make sure I was asleep.
